<div class="grid-mw--1200 hero__footer">
<h2 class="rice-research-header">Rice Research</h2>

<p class="rice-research-subhead"><strong>Advancing Discovery and Innovation</strong></p>

<p>Climate change. Water pollution. Increasing economic and social disparities. Rising rates of cancer and other diseases. The world is facing unprecedented challenges when it comes to human health and prosperity. At Rice, we are at the forefront of research aimed at advancing solutions to these fundamental problems.</p>
</div>
</div>
<style type="text/css">h2.rice-research-header {
  font-family: 'MalloryBlack';
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #fff;
margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

