<div class="blue-column"><img alt="Hand holding a small white pill with text reading 'Could this be the future of pancreatic cancer treatment?'" class="image-responsive lazyload" style="border: #000 1px solid;" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/rice-mag-research-image.webp"></div>
</div>

<div class="res2-column-some-page-wrapper">
<div class="green-column">
<h2 style="color: #13133E;">SPECIAL RESEARCH EDITION</h2>
<!--<img alt="Research Image" class="image-responsive" src="https://magazine.rice.edu/sites/g/files/bxs4576/files/2022-04/rice-magazine-logo-65px.png" />-->

<p class="research-body">Research isn’t just a key driver of our mission — it’s the heartbeat of our contribution to society’s progress. From groundbreaking medical discoveries to innovative engineering solutions, the research and scholarship performed by our talented faculty, postdoctoral fellows and students transforms lives, strengthens our nation’s competitiveness and addresses global challenges.</p>
<a class="responsive-button" href="https://magazine.rice.edu/" target="_blank">Read Rice Magazine<span class="sr-only">(opens in a new window)</span></a></div>
</div>
</div>
