              <div><div class="res3-inst-container-blue">
<section class="res3-container">
<div class="res3-content"><!-- Left Column -->
<div class="res3-left-column">
<h2>Advancing Discovery Through Interdisciplinary Research</h2>

<p>Rice University has focused on key areas of research, showcased through its interdisciplinary institutes and centers. These efforts drive progress in nanoscale science, computing, quantum studies, and collaborative research across biology, chemistry, and engineering. Together, they support excellent education, strengthen research facilities, foster collaboration, and help share scientific knowledge with students and the wider community.</p>
</div>
<!-- Right Column -->

<div class="res3-right-column">

