              <div><div class="grid-mw--1080 ph@m-5">
<div class="page-body__content">
<h2 class="video-header">WHERE OUR RESEARCH DOLLARS GO</h2>

<p style="font-size: 1.35rem;">Rice’s research funding fosters an ecosystem of discovery by supporting direct research costs, graduate student research, and indirect research expenses.</p>

<div class="masonry-grid">
<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Research Project Staffing Costs</h3>
<img alt="Two researchers work in a lab while a student with a red bag walks past." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-1.webp">
<p>Salaries, wages and benefits for researchers, staff and postdocs working on a research project</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Student Summer Stipends</h3>
<img alt="Researcher in a red jacket observes and takes notes next to a tree outdoors." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-2.webp">
<p>Stipends for graduate students and undergraduate students with summer research positions working on a research project</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Research Equipment &amp; Supplies</h3>
<img alt="Laboratory equipment including a microscope, petri dishes, a notepad, and a computer screen displaying an owl graphic." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-3.webp">
<p>Lab equipment and research supplies specific to a research project</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Research &amp; Conference Travel</h3>
<img alt="Presenter speaking to an audience with a bar graph on screen and an airplane graphic above." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-4.webp">
<p>Any travel costs for doing research and also travel to present project findings at conferences</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">SUPPORTING GRADUATE STUDENT RESEARCH</h3>
<img alt="Two scientists in lab coats and gloves discuss research in a hallway." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-5.webp">
<p>Did you know that Rice’s graduate and undergraduate student populations are almost equal?</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Facility Operating Costs</h3>
<img alt="Building infrastructure graphic showing electricity, heating, and cooling systems." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-6.webp">
<p>Utilities, heating and cooling, operations and maintenance expenses for the building...</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Research Data &amp; Computing Infrastructure</h3>
<img alt="Stack of books next to a server rack symbolizing research libraries and data storage." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-7.webp">
<p>Libraries, databases, and computing and data infrastructure integral to doing research</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Administrative Salaries &amp; Expenses</h3>
<img alt="Administrator working on a computer with spreadsheets and database files shown above." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-8.webp">
<p>General expenses and salaries for department, central office and research administrators</p>
</div>

<div class="masonry-item">
<h3 class="masonry-header">Compliance &amp; Safety Costs</h3>
<img alt="Two safety officers in protective suits with gloves, goggles, masks, and boots illustrated." class="image-responsive lazyload" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-04/elena-lacey-rice-spot-9.webp">
<p>General expenses, equipment and salaries for compliance and safety</p>
</div>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 2rem;">Read the full story on <a href="https://magazine.rice.edu/spring-2025/where-our-research-dollars-go" rel="noopener" target="_blank">magazine.rice.edu<span class="sr-only">(opens in a new window)</span></a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
