<div class="grid-mw--1080 ph@m-5">
<div class="page-body__content">
<div class="rr3-mag-container">
<div class="rr3-mag-left-column">
<h2>RICE RESEARCH REVIEW (R3)</h2>

<p class="research-body">At Rice University, research isn’t just what we do — it’s how we shape a better world. For over a century, our commitment to solving global challenges has fueled bold discoveries and real-world impact. Now, this spirit of innovation and service is celebrated in our new biannual publication.</p>
<a class="responsive-button" href="https://research.rice.edu/r3" target="_blank">Read the Fall 2025 Edition</a></div>

<div class="rr3-mag-right-column"><img alt class="image-responsive lazyload" role="presentation" data-src="/sites/g/files/bxs2566/files/2025-09/r3-book-cover-fall-2025.webp"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<style type="text/css">.rr3-mag-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      width: 100%;

    }

.rr3-mag-left-column h2 {
